225c7ca1-8289-49ce-8354-d5e119e8905f',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>Class outings and groups are always welcome at performances. <strong>Why should you organize a group?</strong></p>\n<ul><li>Groups save up to 30% on tickets</li><li>No handling fees on group tickets</li><li>One complimentary ticket per 20 purchased</li></ul><p><strong>Ordering Group Tickets</strong><br />Group rates apply for groups of 10 or more.</p>\n<p>In order to make a reservation, please give the closest estimate of the number of seats that will be needed, complete billing information, phone number and e-mail address. Strawdog has open seating, which means that all audience members will be seated on a first come, first serve basis. However, we will gladly block off seats if requested by a group. Once your order has been confirmed, you will be sent an invoice/contract via email.</p>\n<p><strong>Payment information</strong><br />The balance is due 2 weeks prior to the performance date; the second deposit is due six weeks prior to performance date, depending on the date the order is placed. You may add group tickets based on availability, but please be sure to let us know about any changes in your group numbers as soon as they occur so we can best prepare for your visit.</p>\n<p><strong>Group Rates</strong><br />Group rates are available for all performances with the exception of opening and closing week-end of the show. Group rates and offers are subject to change.</p>\n<p><em><strong>For more information please email our Managing Director at <a href=\"mailto:leahb@strawdog.org?subject=Strawdog%20Theatre%20Company%20-%20Group%20Sales\">leahb@strawdog.org</a></strong></em></p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(105,126,1,'Kamille Dawkins at the Black Tie, Blue Jeans fundraiser.','2019-07-24 03:15:31','2019-0