eshore Drive</strong> and exit on Irving Park Ave. Continue west to turn left on Ravenswood Avenue (just west of the Metra tracks). Turn right on Berenice Avenue. Our theatre will be on your right. OR take <strong>I-94</strong> and exit on Irving Park Ave. Go east on Irving Park, then turn right on Ravenswood Avenue.</p><h2>Parking</h2>\n<p>Parking is available in the lot to the west of the theatre building, against the wall of the theatre. The parking lot is accessible via the alley, which you can access via Byron or Ravenswood. You cannot access the parking lot from Berenice Ave. There is non-permitted street parking on Ravenswood and Berenice Ave. <strong>Do not park in any spots labeled BLACK BEAR ACADEMY—they will tow!</strong></p><h2>Rent Our Space</h2><p>Strawdog\'s beautiful 80 seat black box theatre located at 1802 W Berenice Ave is available to rent! We aim to fill it day and night with Chicago theatre artists who want to help give life to this new basecamp for our work and our community. It\'s a flexible, easily configurable space perfect for performances, staged readings, auditions, rehearsals and other events. Our scene shop is fully equipped with a variety of tools and building space.</p>\n<p>Rental fees for performances, late nights, rehearsals, shop space, and special events vary. Email <a href=\"mailto:rentals@strawdog.org\">rentals@strawdog.org </a>with questions about the space, rates, and availability.</p><h2>Rent Our Stuff!</h2>\n<p>Strawdog has lighting and sound equipment, furniture, instruments, and more available to rent.</p>\n<p>Email <a href=\"mailto:rentals@strawdog.org\">rentals@strawdog.org </a>for rates and availability.</p>\n<p>Examples of available items include:</p>\n<ul><li>10 x Black highboy tables</li><li>20 x Black high Stools</li><li>1 x ETC Ion 2000, compatible with ETC Nomad</li><li>10 x ColorBlast TRX (RGBAW) w/ Power Supply</li><li>6 x Strip Lights</li><li>1 x Panasonic DZ6700U 6000 Lumen WUXGA (1920x1200) DLP projector</li><li>1 x Epson EX-31 2500 Lumen SVGA (800x600) LCD projector</li><li>1 x Piano</li><li>Much, much more. We have a lot of stuff.</li></ul>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(118,139,1,'Performance Space and Rentals','2019-07-25 00:03:05','2019-07-25 00:03:05','87c8080f-cdb7-4d25-8ec3-350099210f25',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'<h2>Location</h2>\n<p>Strawdog\'s 30th season continues in our new home at <strong>1802 West Berenice Avenue</strong>, in Chicago\'s North Center neighborhood.</p>\n<p><strong>Public Transit</strong>: take the <strong>brown line</strong> to the Irving Park Station and exit at the south end of the platform. This will put you on the south side of Irving Park Ave. Go east on Irving Park just ½ block and turn right on Ravenswood (staying on the west side of the Metra tracks) and walk south to Berenice. Our theatre will be on your right.</p>\n<p><strong>By Car</strong>: Take <strong>Lakeshore Drive</strong> and exit on Irving Park Ave. Continue west to turn left on Ravenswood Avenue (just west of the Metra tracks). Turn right on Berenice Avenue. Our theatre will be on your right. OR take <strong>I-94</strong> and exit on Irving Park Ave. Go east on Irving Park, then turn right on Ravenswood Avenue.</p>\n<h2>Parking</h2>\n<p>Parking is available in the lot to the west of the theatre building, against the wall of the theatre. The parking lot is accessible via the alley, which you can access via Byron or Ravenswood. You cannot access the parking lot from Berenice Ave. There is non-permitted street parking on Ravenswood and Berenice Ave. <strong>Do not park in any spots labeled BLACK BEAR ACADEMY—they will tow!</strong></p>\n<h2>Rent Our Space</h2>\n<p>Strawdog\'s beautiful 80 seat black box theatre located at 1802 W Berenice Ave is available to rent! We aim to fill i