on Berenice Avenue. Our theatre will be on your right. OR take <strong>I-94</strong> and exit on Irving Park Ave. Go east on Irving Park, then turn right on Ravenswood Avenue.</p>\n<h4>PARKING</h4>\n<p>Parking is available in the lot to the west of the theatre building, against the wall of the theatre. The parking lot is accessible via the alley, which you can access via Byron or Ravenswood. You cannot access the parking lot from Berenice Ave. There is non-permitted street parking on Ravenswood and Berenice Ave. <strong>Do not park in any spots labeled BLACK BEAR ACADEMY—they will tow!</strong></p><h4>EAT &amp; DRINK IN NORTH CENTER</h4>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.begylebrewing.com/home/\">Begyle Brewery</a><br />800 W Cuyler Ave | (773) 661-6963<br />Straightforward microbrewery &amp; retailer teaming its craft beers with tours &amp; more. Plus they\'re Strawdog\'s beer sponsor!<br /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.brownstonetavern.com/\">Brownstone Tavern</a><br />3937 N Lincoln Ave | (773) 528-3700<br />Spacious neighborhood sports bar featuring outdoor seating &amp; a menu of upscale pub grub.<br /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bigbrickschicago.com/\">Big Bricks</a><br />3832 N Lincoln Ave | (773) 525-5022 <br />Low-key pizzeria serving Chicago staples of beer, thin-crust pizza &amp; BBQ pork with an upscale twist.<br /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://eatorangegarden.com/zgrid/themes/10592/intro/index.jsp\">Orange Garden</a><br />1942 W Irving Park Rd | (773) 525-7479<br />Chinese mainstay for old-school Cantonese cooking in simple rooms with art &amp; artifacts since 1932.<strong><br /></strong></p>\n',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(150,171,1,'Contact Us','2019-07-25 01:01:57','2019-08-08 01:39:33','3ca66faf-a041-4be8-9d83-f94f55b585cd',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'<h2>ADDRESS</h2>\n<p><st