cks</a><br />3832 N Lincoln Ave | (773) 525-5022 <br />Low-key pizzeria serving Chicago staples of beer, thin-crust pizza &amp; BBQ pork with an upscale twist.<br /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://eatorangegarden.com/zgrid/themes/10592/intro/index.jsp\">Orange Garden</a><br />1942 W Irving Park Rd | (773) 525-7479<br />Chinese mainstay for old-school Cantonese cooking in simple rooms with art &amp; artifacts since 1932.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(158,179,1,'Contact Us','2019-07-25 02:41:57','2019-07-25 02:41:57','e3c32490-28f7-4770-9c1d-90126f01019e',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p><strong>Strawdog Theatre Company</strong><br />1802 W Berenice Ave<br />Chicago IL 60613</p><h4>TELEPHONE</h4><p><a href=\"tel:7736441380\">773.644.1380</a></p><h4>EMAIL</h4><figure><a href=\"mailto:boxoffice@strawdog.org?subject=Strawdog%20Theatre%20Company%20-%20Contact\"><img src=\"https://www.strawdog.org/images/envelope_new.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><strong>boxoffice@strawdog.org</strong></a></figure><h4>STAFF</h4><figure><a href=\"mailto:ledahoffmann@strawdog.org?subject=Strawdog%20Theatre%20Company%20-%20Artistic%20Director\"><img src=\"https://www.strawdog.org/images/envelope_new.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /> Artistic Director</a></figure>Leda Hoffmann<figure><a href=\"mailto:charlotte@strawdog.org?subject=Strawdog%20Theatre%20Company%20-%20Managing%20Director\"><img src=\"https://www.strawdog.org/images/envelope_new.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /> Managing Director</a></figure>Charlotte Thomas<figure><a href=\"mailto:cheath@strawdog.org?subject=Strawdog%20Theatre%20Company%20-%20Literary%20Manager\"><img src=\"https://www.strawdog.org/images/envelope_new.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /> Literary Manager</a></figure>Cara Beth Heath<figure><a href=\"mailto:kamille@strawdog.org?subject=Strawdo