reats from intimate partners and acquaintances, this discussion emphasizes: boundary setting, self-respect and the monitoring of relationship dynamics.<br /><br /><strong>Providing Support:</strong> We acknowledge and welcome the potential presence of survivors in the room and recognize that aspects of the workshop may be challenging and sensitive by nature. Support is provided throughout the workshop to anyone, as needed, by a Licensed Clinical Professional Counselor.<br /><br />This course requires no martial arts training, nor extreme physical aptitudes. All skill levels are welcome and encouraged. <br /><br /><a href=\"https://www.chicagomindandbody.com/about-the-founder/\"><strong>Sarah Farris</strong></a> (she/her/hers) works as a therapist and part-time nutrition counselor. She curates healthy lifestyle practices for her clients. She has also expanded a new business \"Chicago Mind &amp; Body\"<br /><br /><a><strong>Cassidy Hill</strong></a> (she/her/hers) As a Certified Personal Trainer with an affinity for martial arts, Cassidy Hill loves helping people feel strong, confident, and capable. Her self defense background involves a hefty combination of Tae Kwon Do, Kung Fu, Hapkido, and Aikido. She is thrilled to be working with By Womxn For Womxn, which offers both a safe space, and a unique environment where we get to lift each other up, showing each other how powerful we can truly be. <br /><br /><a href=\"http://strawdog.org/index.php?shot=mpetro_large.jpg&amp;section=company&amp;person=michaelapetro\"><strong>Michaela Petro</strong></a> (she/her/hers) is an actor and certified trainer of self-defense &amp; rape prevention with the American Women\'s Self-Defense Association (AWSDA). As an ensemble member of Strawdog Theatre Company, one of her core beliefs is serving her community and does so by sharing empowerment skills.</p>','40','https://red.vendini.com/ticket-software.html?t=tix&e=22a03b7c38d433a51f2ac69c3fd10a2a','<p>A new way, led by womxn: learn a three-tiered approach to self-defense for all skill levels.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-07-28 17:00:00','2019-07-28 21:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(240,273,1,'Black Tie, Blue Jeans','2019-07-29 00:14:20','2019-07-29 00:14:20','5ee6f98a-9083-42de-9567-d35f00073db0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>Our super-fun, super-popular annual gala will return in 2020—bigger and better than ever!</p>',NULL,'','<p>Our super-fun, super-popular annual gala will return in 2020—bigger and better than ever!</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(242,275,1,'Sam Hubbard.','2019-07-29 03:59:19','2019-08-08 01:26:22','402678c9-1d35-497c-8886-4a4fe2135d9f',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(243,276,1,'Sam Hubbard','2019-07-29 03:59:29','2019-07-30 23:46:45','1269ecce-ad82-4fb0-8c39-43fa192a5e70',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>Sam Hubbard has appeared in Strawdog’s NEIGHBORHOOD 3: REQUISITION OF DOOM, THE LONG CHRISTMAS RIDE HOME, CYMBELINE, and DAMASCUS. He’s directed fights for many, many Strawdog productions, including GREAT EXPECTATIONS, BARBECUE, AFTER MISS JULIE, CHARLES IVES TAKE ME HOME, ROBIN HOOD, QUIZ SHOW, and more.</p>\n<p>Acting credits include THE BOOK OF WILL (Northlight Theatre), A LOSS OF ROSES and PLAYBOY OF THE WESTERN WORLD (Raven Theatre), THE DIARY OF ANNE FRANK (Writers Theatre), CYMBELINE and HAMLET (Michigan Shakespeare Festival), productions with The Factory, Oak Park Festival Theatre, and Jackalope, and understudy roles at Steppenwolf, Chicag