\n<p><strong>By Car</strong>: Take Lakeshore Drive and exit on Irving Park Ave. Continue west to turn left on Ravenswood Avenue (just west of the Metra tracks). Turn right on Berenice Avenue. Our theatre will be on your right. OR take I-94 and exit on Irving Park Ave. Go east on Irving Park, then turn right on Ravenswood Avenue.</p>\n<h2 id=\"parking\">Parking</h2>\n<p>Parking is available in the lot to the west of the theatre building, against the wall of the theatre. The parking lot is accessible via the alley, which you can access via Byron or Ravenswood. You cannot access the parking lot from Berenice Ave. There is non-permitted street parking on Ravenswood and Berenice Ave. <strong>Do not park in any spots labeled BLACK BEAR ACADEMY—they will tow!</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"seating\">Seating Policy</h2>\n<p>Seating is general admission. The house opens 15 minutes before show time.<br /></p>\n<p>Patrons who arrive late will be seated at the discretion of the House Manager. Not all Strawdog productions allow late seating. We recommend that you arrive at the venue early to make sure you are able to attend the production.</p>\n<h2 id=\"northcenter\">Eat &amp; Drink in North Center</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.begylebrewing.com/home/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><strong>Begyle Brewery</strong></a><br />800 W Cuyler Ave | (773) 661-6963<br />Straightforward microbrewery &amp; retailer teaming its craft beers with tours &amp; more. Plus they\'re Strawdog’s beer sponsor!<br /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.brownstonetavern.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><strong>Brownstone Tavern</strong></a><br />3937 N Lincoln Ave | (773) 528-3700<br />Spacious neighborhood sports bar featuring outdoor seating &amp; a menu of upscale pub grub.<br /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bigbrickschicago.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><strong>Big Bricks</strong></a><br />3832 N Lincoln Ave | (773) 525-5022 <br />Low-key pizzeria serving Chicago staples of beer, thin-crust pizza &amp; BBQ pork with an upscale twist.<br /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://eatorangegarden.com/zgrid/themes/10592/intro/index.jsp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><strong>Orange Garden</strong></a><br />1942 W Irving Park Rd | (773) 525-7479<br />Chinese mainstay since 1932 for old-school Cantonese cooking in simple rooms with art &amp; artifacts.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'<h1>Plan Your Visit<br /></h1>\n<ul><li><a href=\"#purchasing\">Purchasing Tickets</a></li><li><a href=\"#ticket\">Ticket Exchange</a></li><li><a href=\"#gettinghere\">Getting Here</a></li><li><a href=\"#parking\">Parking</a></li><li><a href=\"#seating\">Seating Policy</a></li><li><a href=\"#northcenter\">Eat &amp; Drink in North Center</a></li></ul>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(1047,2190,1,'Shows','2019-08-07 03:10:35','2019-08-07 03:10:35','161ef3d9-cfc2-4c7d-87e0-845642184d93',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Mauris augue neque gravida in. Massa tempor nec feugiat nisl pretium fusce id. At in tellus integer feugiat scelerisque varius morbi. Lectus mauris ultrices eros in cursus. Molestie nunc non blandit massa enim nec. Gravida dictum fusce ut placerat orci nulla pellentesque. Lobortis scelerisque fermentum dui faucibus. Tortor aliquam nulla facilisi cras fermentum odio eu feugiat pretium. Morbi tristique senectus et netus et malesuada fames. Proin sagittis nisl rhoncus mattis rhoncus urna. Eu feugiat pretium nibh ipsum. Turpis egestas maecenas pharetra convallis. Adipiscing at in tellus integer feugiat scelerisque varius morbi. Tellus integer feugiat scelerisque varius morbi enim. Lorem ipsum 